Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:00.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,拜…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,从我嘴里说出「拜拜」感觉很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.92,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,可恶 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,那明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.19,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:33.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,山田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,明天是星期六啊
